data.description: Escape to the tranquility of Bethpage, TN, where rustic charm meets modern comfort in this stunning Barndominium situated on a spacious 1-acre lot. Discover the perfect blend of country living and contemporary design, offering a unique lifestyle that combines comfort, style, and safety. Unleash your creativity or tackle DIY projects in the expansive workshop, complete with ample storage and workspace for your tools and hobbies. Rest easy knowing you have a secure storm bunker, ensuring your family's safety during severe weather. Peace of mind is just steps away. Located in the heart of Bethpage, TN, enjoy the serenity of rural living while still being close to essential amenities, schools, and community attractions.
